<h2>What's New</h2>

<h3>Fixed</h3>
<ul>
<li>Fix "Check Now" button disappearing after update check (now stays visible with result text)</li>
<li>Fix update check results not auto-dismissing for all result types</li>
<li>Fix initial canCheckForUpdates state not syncing on app launch</li>
</ul>

<h3>Changed</h3>
<ul>
<li>Increase automatic update check frequency from 24 hours to 4 hours</li>
</ul>

